title: FANTOM Update: Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap - Mass Update
body:
Intro: This is a vote to update the collateral factors and collateral caps on the FANTOM C.R.E.A.M. market.

Proposal: Listing Committee

Rational: Update and improve FANTOM market.

For:
Update Collateral Factors and Collateral Caps EXACTLY as displayed in sheets (FTM tab)— https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zZlTitPtIO-JMXDq_G19ScBpScbYE3q6WvXSHygykGY/edit#gid=0

Against:
Do not make any changes to FANTOM market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
